videos.description: Joel Berry II knocks down a 3-pointer after the ball reaches nearly every player on the floor for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Great ball movement by UNC leads to long triple

videos.description: Braian Angola has the hot hand beyond the arc for Florida State, but the Seminoles have 8 three-balls before the half.
videos.headline: Angola accounts for 3 of Seminoles' 8 threes in first half

videos.description: Joel Berry II knocks down a 3 to tie the score at 58 after North Carolina was down by 11 points to Florida State at halftime.
videos.headline: Berry II buries a 3-pointer to tie score

videos.description: Theo Pinson receives a great pass form Cameron Johnson and draws the foul while making the difficult layup.
videos.headline: Pinson battles for difficult and-1

videos.description: CJ Walker battles on the ground for the ball and flips it up to M.J.Walker who throws down a ferocious one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Walker's diving steal leads to huge slam

videos.description: C.J. Walker waits in the corner for the pass from Terance Mann and drains the open three to push the Seminoles' lead to 9.
videos.headline: Walker knocks down 4th 3-pointer

videos.description: Joel Berry II corrals the errant pass and drops a long 3-pointer in the face of the Seminoles to get the Heels within 4.
videos.headline: Berry II stays hot from distance with his 3rd long ball

videos.description: Theo Pinson reads the cross-court pass perfectly and steals it and then passes to the hot-hand Joel Berry II who buries a 3.
videos.headline: Berry II capitalizes on huge steal with another 3-pointer

videos.description: North Carolina's last chance to win the game comes up short and the Seminoles get the win 81-80.
videos.headline: Tar Heels' final play comes up short
